another aspect of baby algebra,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:09:46.890 --> 00:09:49.950
which is very important for public&nbsp;
school and high school mathematics:&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:09:49.950 --> 00:09:58.620
the issue of identities. I hope you'll join me for&nbsp;
that. I'm Norman Wildberger. Thanks for listening.

